860
01:01:42,400 --> 01:01:44,528
喔, 天啊.
Oh, my goodness.

861
01:01:53,720 --> 01:01:54,607
喬克.
Jock.

862
01:01:54,760 --> 01:01:56,250
尼克.
Nick.

863
01:01:56,440 --> 01:01:58,010
