1169
01:34:30,600 --> 01:34:32,762
你應該知道我剛剛宣讀的你的權利?
Do you understand these rights as I have read them to you?

1170
01:34:39,840 --> 01:34:41,922
<i>我把懷亞特和哥達德交給聯邦調查局了.</i>
ADAM: I handed the Feds Wyatt and Goddard.

1171
01:34:43,680 --> 01:34:46,286
<i>他們將有很長一段時間看不到明媚的陽光了.</i>
They won't be seeing light for a vert long time.

1172
01:34:47,520 --> 01:34:50,285
<i>茱蒂絲和米徹姆得到他們應有的報應</i>
Judith and Meachum got what they deserved too.

1173
01:34:52,680 --> 01:34:55,524
<i>而我, 很幸運.</i>
As for me, I got lucky.

1174
01:34:55,680 --> 01:34:58,206
<i>因為我的合作所以被聯邦調查局放過一馬.</i>
The Feds cut me a break for my cooperation.

1175
01:34:58,680 --> 01:34:59,647
不...
No...

1176
01:35:08,720 --> 01:35:12,088
<i>有些事情現在想來其實也沒那麼重要..</i>
ADAM: The things I thought I wanted don't seem so important anymore.

1177
01:35:14,160 --> 01:35:15,685
<i>我從錯誤中學習了正確,還有...</i>
I do know right from wrong, and...

1178
01:35:17,480 --> 01:35:20,131
<i>...我必須為我長期以來的欺?道歉.</i>
...I'm sorrt it took me so long to act on it.

1179
01:35:21,960 --> 01:35:25,009
<i>我只想讓你知道</i>
ADAM (OVER VOICE MAIL): I just want you to know that

1180
01:35:25,160 --> 01:35:27,401
<i>我不想做任何對不起你的事兒..</i>
I never wanted to do any of this to you.

1181
01:35:30,400 --> 01:35:32,402
<i>我只希望有一天我能處理好一切.</i>
I hope one day I can make things right.

1182
01:35:38,440 --> 01:35:39,680
<i>對不起, 艾瑪.</i>
I'm sorrt, Emma.

1183
01:35:51,760 --> 01:35:52,966
謝謝.
Thanks.

1184
01:35:54,760 --> 01:35:56,842
快!快!快!快!
Go, go, go, go! Go! Go! Go!

1185
01:35:57,080 --> 01:35:58,923
快跑, 快跑!
Run, run!

1186
01:35:59,087 --> 01:36:00,046
(LAUGHS)

1187
01:36:05,520 --> 01:36:06,567
怎麼?
What?

1188
01:36:09,760 --> 01:36:12,411
我有告訴過你,你是對的嗎?
Did I ever tell you, you were right?

1189
01:36:13,760 --> 01:36:15,125
關於什麼?
About what?

1190
01:36:16,160 --> 01:36:17,491
一切.
Everything.

1191
01:36:21,560 --> 01:36:23,244
我的意思是.
I mean that.

1192
01:36:23,400 --> 01:36:25,289
很抱歉我以前沒聽進去.
I'm sorry I didn't listen to you.

1193
01:36:41,240 --> 01:36:43,083
那女孩怎麼樣了?
How's it going with that girl?

1194
01:36:45,560 --> 01:36:46,971
她不肯和我說話.
Well, she won't talk to me.

1195
01:36:48,680 --> 01:36:50,762
在結束前是不會結束的,比賽終了才知輸贏.
It ain't over till it's over.

1196
01:36:51,920 --> 01:36:55,561
你知道我和你媽約會了多久嗎？?
You know how long it took me to get a date with your mother?

1197
01:36:56,520 --> 01:36:57,760
多久?
How long?

1198
01:37:00,680 --> 01:37:02,762
很久.
(LAUGHS) A long time.

1199
01:37:04,960 --> 01:37:08,123
我看起來都比你現在好看多了.
And I was much better-iooking then than you are now.

1200
01:37:08,280 --> 01:37:11,090
- 真的嗎? - 噢耶.
- Oh, is that right? - Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.

1201
01:37:11,243 --> 01:37:14,829
- (FATHER LAUGHS) - (CHILDREN YELLING)

1202
01:37:19,280 --> 01:37:22,489
你去哪兒？地鐵在這邊
Where you going? The subway is this way.

1203
01:37:22,640 --> 01:37:24,927
我有更快的交通工具,快過來.
I got a faster ride. Come on.

1204
01:37:26,633 --> 01:37:27,967
(CAR ALARM CHIRPS)

1205
01:37:31,840 --> 01:37:33,683
我以為我們徹底完了?
I thought we were done with this shit?

1206
01:37:33,840 --> 01:37:35,808
這是租的啦老爸,我租了一天
It's a rental, Dad. I got it for the day.

1207
01:37:35,960 --> 01:37:38,964
哦,真的嗎?好啦,讓我們找點樂子去
Oh, yeah? Well, then, let's have some fun.

1208
01:37:40,080 --> 01:37:42,845
<i>一個能讓你不迷失自己的方法..</i>
ADAM: One way to remember who you are...

1209
01:37:43,040 --> 01:37:45,407
你怎麼開這玩意兒的?
How do you open this thing?

1210
01:37:45,560 --> 01:37:47,847
<i>就是銘記你的英雄們是誰？.</i>
ADAM: ...is to remember who your heroes are.

1211
01:37:49,614 --> 01:37:51,615
(TIRES SCREECH, ENGINE RACES)

1212
01:37:51,783 --> 01:37:53,200
($ THE BABIES: "MOONLIGHT MILE")

1213
01:38:00,360 --> 01:38:02,283
<i>我已經在做這件事了.</i>
I'm doing things my way now.

1214
01:38:02,480 --> 01:38:05,165
<i>萬丈高樓平地起.</i>
Building from the ground up.

1215
01:38:05,320 --> 01:38:07,482
<i>羅馬不是一天造成的.</i>
There are no shortcuts.

1216
01:38:08,040 --> 01:38:09,804
我的天呀,你在搞什麼?
Oh my God, what are you doing?

1217
01:38:09,960 --> 01:38:12,122
- 啥?我搞砸了. - 我們有好多事兒要忙的.
- What? I messed it up. - We have a lot of things to do.

1218
01:38:12,320 --> 01:38:13,970
- 來吧! - 好吧, 做什麼!
- Come on! - All right, Jesus!

1219
01:38:17,880 --> 01:38:19,120
嗨. 艾瑪詹寧斯.
Hi. Emma Jennings.

1220
01:38:19,280 --> 01:38:21,044
稍等.
One second.

1221
01:38:23,240 --> 01:38:25,607
艾登, 你有客人
Adam, you have a visitor.

1222
01:38:37,200 --> 01:38:38,326
嘿.
Hey.

1223
01:38:39,920 --> 01:38:41,365
嗨.
Hi.

1224
01:38:44,480 --> 01:38:47,165
你這裡看起來不錯.
Nice place you have here.

1225
01:38:47,320 --> 01:38:49,243
我的意思是, 為了布魯克林.
I mean, for Brooklyn.

1226
01:38:51,040 --> 01:38:53,168
非常榮幸你能來.
I'm glad you came.

1227
01:38:53,360 --> 01:38:56,967
一直收到一個創新公司的工作邀請e-mail.
Kept getting e-mails about a job offer at a brand-new startup company.

1228
01:38:58,800 --> 01:39:00,404
卻沒看見他們真來找我...
Why I didn't see that coming...

1229
01:39:00,560 --> 01:39:03,723
是啊,我們...
Yeah, we, uh...

1230
01:39:03,880 --> 01:39:06,281
我們真的需要你這樣的人才.
We really need you here.

1231
01:39:06,960 --> 01:39:08,450
你們請不起我的.
You couldn't afford me.

1232
01:39:08,600 --> 01:39:10,921
有大量的股票可得
Lots of stock options.

1233
01:39:14,080 --> 01:39:16,082
那必須做的更好才行.
You have to do better than that.

1234
01:39:18,960 --> 01:39:20,405
沒問題.
OK.

1235
01:39:25,680 --> 01:39:27,921
我真的需要你.
I need you here.

1236
01:39:39,440 --> 01:39:40,930
讓我再想想.
I'll think about it.

1237
01:39:52,720 --> 01:39:53,846
來吧,我請你喝杯東西.
Come on, let me buy you a drink.

1238
01:39:54,000 --> 01:39:55,843
你說你對鄉巴佬男孩有好感
You said you had a thing for bridge-and-tunnel.

1239
01:39:56,000 --> 01:39:58,128
你說過的. 艾瑪.
Your words. Emma.

1240
01:40:01,040 --> 01:40:03,725
至少我應該感謝你考慮我提供的工作邀請?
Can I at least thank you for considering my offer?

1241
01:40:19,848 --> 01:40:22,516
($ EMPIRE OF THE SUN: "ALIVE (ZEDD REMIX)")

1242
01:40:29,880 --> 01:40:31,006
謝謝.
Thank you.

1243
01:40:35,320 --> 01:40:37,561
<i>我喜歡經過那座橋.</i>
ADAM: I like being across the bridge.

1244
01:40:38,360 --> 01:40:41,887
<i>有一種回家的感覺~.</i>
Over here, it feels like home.

1245
01:40:42,120 --> 01:40:44,955
($ EMPIRE OF THE SUN: "ALIVE (ZEDD REMIX)")

